<paragraph id="BF34F77FB4B15722B69E417081464CF0" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Named in honor of Dr Wojciech Jerzy Pulawski, Curator of Entomology, Emeritus, at CAS, the person who collected the specimen from Jamaica.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
